  <h2>
    <span class="">喜欢读&#34;最純潔的種族&#34;的人也喜欢</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


  <div class="content clearfix">
      
      <dl class="">
        <dt>
            <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/11637051/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '11637051', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})"><img class="m_sub_img" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/spic/s11317899.jpg"/></a>
        </dt>
        <dd>
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/11637051/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '11637051', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})" class="">
            平壤水族馆
          </a>
        </dd>
      </dl>
      
      <dl class="">
        <dt>
            <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/10533895/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '10533895', 'pos': 1, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})"><img class="m_sub_img" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/spic/s8923438.jpg"/></a>
